{"id":215043,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2012/03/global-voices-影片：巴拿马原住民纳索族人寻求国际协助抵/","date":"2012-03-12T11:12:18Z","modified":"2012-03-12T11:12:18Z","title":"Global Voices | 影片：巴拿马原住民纳索族人寻求国际协助抵制大坝工程","content":"<p><p>在以多媒体提倡原住民与环境议题读艺术团体<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://www.selvarica.com/english/Selva_Rica/Costa_Rica.html\" href=\"http://www.selvarica.com/english/Selva_Rica/Costa_Rica.html\">SelvaRica</a>所拍摄的<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://vimeo.com/37544203\" href=\"http://vimeo.com/37544203\">这部影片</a>中，一位来自巴拿马纳索族的原住民妇女寻求国际社群协助以施压、阻止一项在他们土地上的大坝工程。这个大坝会冲毁他们的林地并改变他们传统的生活模式，以他们视之为二次掠夺的方式冲击其文化：第一次他们因为金矿遭到迫害，今天则是因为他们的自然资源。</p>\n<div>校对：<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"使用者:Portnoy\" href=\"http://proj.daodin.net/mediawiki/index.php/%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E8%80E5%BD%B1%E7%89%87%EF%BC%9A%E5%B7%B4%E6%8B%BF%E9%A9%AC%E5%8E%9F%E4%BD%8F%E6%B0%91%E7%BA%B3%E7%B4%A2%E6%97%8F%E4%BA%BA%E5%AF%BB%E6%B1%82%E5%9B%BD%E9%99%85%E5%8D%8F%E5%8A%A9%E6%8A%B5%E5%88%B6%E5%A4%A7%E5%9D%9D%E5%B7%A5%E7%A8%8B&#038;url=http%3A%2F%2Fzh.globalvoicesonline.org%2Fhans%2F2012%2F03%2F12%2F10554%2F&#038;description=&#038;via=sticker\" title=\"HEMiDEMi\"><span>HEMiDEMi</span></a> · <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://myshare.url.com.tw/index.php?func=newurl&#038;url=http%3A%2F%2Fzh.globalvoicesonline.org%2Fhans%2F2012%2F03%2F12%2F10554%2F&#038;desc=%E5%BD%B1%E7%89%87%EF%BC%9A%E5%B7%B4%E6%8B%BF%E9%A9%AC%E5%8E%9F%E4%BD%8F%E6%B0%91%E7%BA%B3%E7%B4%A2%E6%97%8F%E4%BA%BA%E5%AF%BB%E6%B1%82%E5%9B%BD%E9%99%85%E5%8D%8F%E5%8A%A9%E6%8A%B5%E5%88%B6%E5%A4%A7%E5%9D%9D%E5%B7%A5%E7%A8%8B\" title=\"MyShare\"><span>MyShare</span></a> · <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.shouker.com/%22%20onclick=20js=document.createElement%20(\" title=\"Shouker\"><span>Shouker</span></a> · <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.facebook.com/share.php?u=http%3A%2F%2Fzh.globalvoicesonline.org%2Fhans%2F2012%2F03%2F12%2F10554%2F\" title=\"facebook\"><span>facebook</span></a> · <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://twitter.com/share?url=ht